		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Suitable numbers are available in the Yar's Revenge source code (look near the bottom, starting at line #2685).  Note that they are upside down, which is typical of graphics assets in Atari 2600 games (makes them easier to feed into the TIA during hblank).

		

